Key Match Events: Rohit Sharma hit a century in the match
Rinku Singh scored 69 not out with 6 sixes
Gulbadin Naib scored 55 not out with 4 sixes in the Super Over
Mohammad Nabi scored 34 with 3 sixes in the Super Over
Ravi Bishnoi claimed both wickets in the second Super Over
Post-Match Reflections: Rohit Sharma expressed pride in the team's resilience after the match
The coach highlighted the victory as a pivotal moment in their series win
Miscellaneous Highlights: The match had two Super Overs, a first in T20Is
Rohit Sharma's century was the fifth fastest in T20Is
Rinku Singh hit half-a-dozen sixes in the last three balls of the innings
